                     <interp inst="t18260511-116-person684" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Bow-street patrol. Grunett<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182605110052"></xptr>told me of this circumstance - I went with him and took the prisoners; I found the beads in How's pocket.</p>
